  -----------------------------------------------------------------------
  **pip-audit connection:** Run pip-audit -r requirements_vulnerable.txt
  on your VM. For each HIGH or CRITICAL finding, apply the three-step
  triage above: read the CVSS vector for the CVE on nvd.nist.gov, assess
  exploitability in a typical Flask deployment, identify the fix version
  in the pip-audit output. Which findings in requirements_vulnerable.txt
  are exploitable with AV:N/PR:N --- and which require conditions your
  application does not have?

  -----------------------------------------------------------------------
